WeatherFetcher - Class in data
WeatherFetcher will connect and request an XML with appropriate configurations from a weather API, to parse through and receive temperature from a specific city.
WeatherFetcher() - Constructor for class data.WeatherFetcher
 
Window - Class in gui
Window will act as the GUI, have buttons, lists of cities and the result from the weather api.
Window(Fetcher) - Constructor for class gui.Window
Constructor Will set up the gui with spring layout and display the window for the user with the dropdown menus, having the content (Cities, hours, cache minutes) we want.
